Alias MyB- B-
Alias MyB+ B+
ChargeConj MyB- MyB+

Alias MyD0 D0
Alias Myanti-D0 anti-D0
ChargeConj MyD0 Myanti-D0

Alias Myrho- rho-
Alias Myrho+ rho+
ChargeConj Myrho- Myrho+

# Upsilon(4S) decay
Decay Upsilon(4S)
0.500 MyB- B+   VSS;
0.500 B- MyB+   VSS;
Enddecay

Decay MyB-
1.000 Myrho- MyD0     SVS;
Enddecay
CDecay MyB+

Decay MyD0
1.000 K- pi+  pi0 D_DALITZ;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-D0

Decay Myrho-
1.000 pi- pi0 VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay Myrho+

End


